{"id": 3017, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你觉得啥样的外出算真正的「出门」？", "description": "在「即便宅在家，所有需求也能被满足」成为日常的情况下，你是怎么看待「出门」（以及与之相关的种种社交）在生活中的意义的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 4822, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190928175423uHwzCEGPVLI45TJK.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-28T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5940, "title": "现如今你觉得啥样的外出算真正的「出门」？", "content": "现如今你觉得啥样的外出才算真正的「出门」？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 347433, "content": "只要走出家门，哪怕倒个垃圾拿个快递也算", "image": "img/option/option/20190928171830s9jlkOSDrgRfhaLM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347434, "content": "必须是有明确目标的外出，比如购物、聚会", "image": "img/option/option/20190928172124Lc3qm908YHSA71wa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347435, "content": "“不带目的”的出门，比如随便走走散心", "image": "img/option/option/20190928172415W4DRLQA8jbtoTuKY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347436, "content": "得是有跟人说过话的那种，全程零线下社交的不算", "image": "img/option/option/2019092817283787JWDRgMQpiCTeU2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347437, "content": "除了上学/上班，其他的出行都可以算", "image": "img/option/option/20190928173254PC5w1ayLtbF3W8Tv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347438, "content": "只有旅游对我来讲才算出门，其他都不算", "image": "img/option/option/20190928173433CYu6ld08EimsfBRM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347440, "content": "没有全程玩手机的出行才算，否则跟自己在家没区别", "image": "img/option/option/20190928173848NaenHMfO8PwSgJBo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347441, "content": "都不是，我有自己特别的定义", "image": "img/option/option/20190928173947eiE6pStyn13gAWam.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}